snippet.title: Cyber Citizen Shockman 3: The Princess from Another World - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Cyber Citizen Shockman 3: The Princess from Another World is a classic 2D action platformer developed by Shinyuden. After Sonya wins a big prize in the lottery and heads to the tropics for much-needed relaxation, chaos ensues as strange starships attack the city from the heavens. Play through a big variety of stages that include platform stages as well as scrolling shooting stages alone or with a friend in 2-player mode.

Cyber Citizen Shockman 3: The Princess from Another World is launching on May 3 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Nintendo Switch.
